      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i need some help with a candidate rejection email. we had a guy named Marcus who made it all the way to the final round for a senior dev position here in austin. he was actually really good and had great technical skills, but we decided to go with someone who had a bit more experience with distributed systems. i want the email to be professional and kind since he was a strong contender, but still firm that we aren't moving forward. can you draft something for me?",
